        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Fann', 3: 'I grew up in this town. Nobody knows the people here better than I do. The Babylonia outsiders will have a hard time here...', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 65,
        "ActionId": 65,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Daemon', 3: 'The Forsaken troops will soon pass through here. Since you have helped me, you are our friend. Rest assured that we will keep the locals unbothered.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 66,
        "ActionId": 66,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Fann', 3: 'I don\\'t care about the uninvited outsiders. It\\'ll be great if you can drive them both away... But no matter what, I won\\'t let anything harm this town. This is the last thing that can remind me of Mother.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 67,
        "ActionId": 67,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Daemon', 3: 'That\\'s easy, but I still don\\'t know about your father... He seems to want this town to remain neutral.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 68,
        "ActionId": 68,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Daemon', 3: 'We warned him many times, but he refuses to give in... He really has no clue who is providing shelter for this town.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 69,
        "ActionId": 69,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Due to their cooperative relationship, the Forsaken camp has been setting up gates to protect New Oakley from Corrupted for years.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 70,
        "ActionId": 70,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '2', 2: '5'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 71,
        "ActionId": 71,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Fann', 3: 'He only clings to those old-fashioned ideals like neutrality and freedom... He must have forgotten how Mother died long ago.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 72,
        "ActionId": 72,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Daemon looks at Fann with a hint of a smile. To him, those people with resentment cannot be any easier to control.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 73,
        "ActionId": 73,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Daemon', 3: 'As long as things can go smoothly this time, I\\'ll recommend you to Generalissimo. You\\'ll be able to join the Forsaken and seek revenge against Babylonia...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 74,
        "ActionId": 74,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 75,
        "ActionId": 75,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Fann', 3: 'Revenge against Babylonia... Is that really possible?', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 76,
        "ActionId": 76,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Daemon', 3: 'We, the Forsakens, are just like you. Every single one of us hates Babylonia for some reason. After Generalissimo joined us, we have also been secretly accepting the victims of Babylonia.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 77,
        "ActionId": 77,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 78,
        "ActionId": 78,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Daemon', 3: 'Soon, we will grow into a formidable power... Those hypocrites in Babylonia won\\'t even be able to imagine what\\'s coming for them.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 79,
        "ActionId": 79,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Daemon points at the faraway tower glowing in blue light. There is a sharp gleam in his eyes.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 80,
        "ActionId": 80,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Daemon', 3: 'We deserve a place in the area under that light, but Babylonia has taken it all away.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 81,
        "ActionId": 81,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Fann', 3: 'Are the Forsakens going to attack the Clean Zone...?!', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 82,
        "ActionId": 82,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 83,
        "ActionId": 83,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Daemon', 3: 'Correct, and this town acts as a crucial gate near the Clean Zone without the worries about Corrupted interference. As long as you can allow the Forsaken troops to pass, our plan will succeed.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 84,
        "ActionId": 84,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Daemon squints at Noctis, who is still wasting effort on his futile investigation.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 85,
        "ActionId": 85,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Daemon', 3: 'But right now, these two from Babylonia are our greatest obstacle. It will be a lot of trouble if they discover our plan before it is executed.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 86,
        "ActionId": 86,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Fann', 3: 'Fine. Those scums always disgrace this town, but now would be a good time to make use of them.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 87,
        "ActionId": 87,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Daemon', 3: 'Excellent idea. If the locals here take action, those Babylonia people would probably hold back due to their hypocritical rules.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 88,
        "ActionId": 88,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Fann signals at a few thugs hiding in a shadowy corner.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 89,
        "ActionId": 89,
