    },
    {
        "Id": 98,
        "ActionId": 98,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": "DialogEnable",
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Feeling extremely bored in the room, you cannot figure out what to do. From what you have heard in the terminal, Noctis seems to have no progress either.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 99,
        "ActionId": 99,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Sigh...', 3: '100'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 100,
        "ActionId": 100,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'You cannot help but let out a sigh. It seems like an eternity since the last time you felt so powerless. Once again, you realize your limit as a commandant.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 101,
        "ActionId": 101,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 401,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '2', 2: '2626'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 102,
        "ActionId": 102,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Right then, someone knocks on the door slowly and steadily. You take off the terminal and instinctively reach under the pillow, where the pistol is hidden.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 103,
        "ActionId": 103,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Who is it...?', 3: '104'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 104,
        "ActionId": 104,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 401,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '2', 2: '754'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 105,
        "ActionId": 105,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 201,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '500692'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 106,
        "ActionId": 106,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 3: 'Without waiting for a response, the door is pushed open, and a burly man walks in assuredly, followed by several retinues.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 107,
        "ActionId": 107,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Mr... Max, what can I do for you?', 3: '108'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 108,
        "ActionId": 108,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Max', 3: 'You are a commandant of Babylonia. A smart person.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 109,
        "ActionId": 109,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Max sits down on a chair, handing his cane to one of his followers.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 110,
        "ActionId": 110,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'I am a commandant, but I may not be that smart.', 3: '111'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 111,
        "ActionId": 111,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'He seems not surprised at the absence of Noctis, indicating that he must have picked this time when Noctis is not around.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 112,
        "ActionId": 112,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Max', 3: 'Then I hope your unintelligence won\\'t bring you too much trouble... The rules you are used to do not work here.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 113,
        "ActionId": 113,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Max', 3: 'This place is a haven for criminals, thugs, scumbags, and people who couldn\\'t make it anywhere else... These people, well, will not surprise anyone if they suddenly lose their lives the next moment.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 114,
        "ActionId": 114,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Are you trying to get us out of here?', 3: '115'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 115,
        "ActionId": 115,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Max', 3: 'That Construct probably has some reason to stay. But I can tell that you are different...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 116,
        "ActionId": 116,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'He glances at the communicator you were working on just now. The screen still shows a Babylonia message title.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 117,
        "ActionId": 117,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Max', 3: 'You still want to return to Babylonia, don\\'t you?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 118,
        "ActionId": 118,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'That is why he seizes this moment and tries to convince you.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 119,
        "ActionId": 119,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Thanks for the advice, but unfortunately, I\\'m probably also a criminal now.', 3: '120'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 120,
        "ActionId": 120,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'If you fail to find Daemon, you will not be able to explain why you went solo. Your joint operation with Noctis, who was a suspect, can only be interpreted as attempting to defect.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 121,
        "ActionId": 121,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '5'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 122,
        "ActionId": 122,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Max', 3: 'Even if you stay here, you won\\'t find anything... Like I said, you are not welcome here. This place is full of...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 123,
        "ActionId": 123,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 502,
